tant;text-align:left;letter-spacing:-0.01em!important">A few weeks ago some=
one at the start of their career was telling me how pleased she was that sh=
e had just got her first full-time, salaried job. It led to a interesting c=
onversation about money and wealth. She was now making enough to cover her =
