ow, if you started with $1,000 and invested $1,000 per month into your inve=
stment burrito, you=E2=80=99d end up $2.5 million in 40 years. In 50 years,=
 at the same rate of investment, you=E2=80=99d end up with over $5 million =
bucks. Which means you=E2=80=99d have turned the $600,000 (the principle) i=
nto $5 million.</em></p>

<p dir=3D"ltr" style=3D"margin:10px 0;padding:0;margin-bottom:20px;color:#1=
