t;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6!important;text-align:left;letter-spacing:-=
0.01em!important">If you started at 20 years old, by 60 you=E2=80=99d be ve=
ry much financially independent investing $1,000 per month into the market.=
 This is how money magically makes more money. Obviously markets spike and =
